               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17861213-124-cd623" type="crimeDate">2d of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861213-124-off622 t17861213-124-cd623"></join>, one watch, inside case made of metal, and the outside tortoiseshell, value 10 s. two brass keys, value 2 d. a seal, value 6 d. a chain, value 2 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17861213-124-victim1205" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Askew
                  <interp inst="t17861213-124-victim1205" type="surname" value="Askew"></interp>
